{"tid":337543,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"返HKTV暑期工比人罰錢賠尿袋","createTime":"2017-07-27T11:41:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-03T10:38:22.000Z","uid":94044,"like":773,"dislike":142,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a0d200b01b410ef9ccc97a571375c38cc06a8fb9","tid":337543,"uid":94044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T11:41:10.000Z","msg":"幫朋友開 <br />\n我FD就做緊HKTV既倉務員(暑期工)<br />\n佢平日既工作就係用部公司比既手機(連barcode機) 跟單執貨 <br />\n咁開工個陣佢會比埋尿袋廢事部機做做下冇電<br />\n收工個陣一次過還番<br />\n執完一張單既貨會入落個箱到比PACKING既部門 再分貨<br />\n<br />\n咁佢完單入箱個陣唔小心放埋個尿袋落箱送左去PACKING<br />\n但其實送到PACKING係每次都好易發視搵得到 尿袋入埋箱佢唔係第一個<br />\n咁間公司就好ON9 有條規則話如果收工還唔到尿袋 當你整唔見個尿袋<br />\n你就要賠返個尿袋比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n既然都搵得返 點解要賠呀 扣人工都合理D丫 家下要人捐成個尿袋比佢 間公司知唔知咩叫唔見左野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :  乞兒公司ON9規則 搵得返賠佢老味最多咪唔做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 公司規則要跟足 樓主未返過工"},{"pid":"40f989e64d13e9304da7af6142c244bde5eb7791","tid":337543,"uid":82532,"like":110,"dislike":2,"score":108,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T11:42:33.000Z","msg":"暑期工, 最多咪唔撈"},{"pid":"e0f4d8976ceb00af43236cae3148abbd99eb4196","tid":337543,"uid":118895,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T11:42:49.000Z","msg":"俐伸前排翻過 啲規矩真係好19"},{"pid":"ddeaf81c3c138b15763eab70f57a13659e177e92","tid":337543,"uid":94044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T11:51:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd2a549f2abb40ce090b44b4c4eeab07ab144be","tid":337543,"uid":38456,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T11:54:42.000Z","msg":"屙d尿俾佢"},{"pid":"53fe9233e5eab4680032c3bce7105ef9f00e5cc5","tid":337543,"uid":94044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:23:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f89f85566dca1c2542ecfb6f7b19a9daf78f03","tid":337543,"uid":115451,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:28:27.000Z","msg":"咁小事都上黎問"},{"pid":"af50fbd5ba0d20ad2fe2b52a1edbe525cd3986f6","tid":337543,"uid":13638,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:28:42.000Z","msg":"負皮比樓豬<br />\n但係你係幫朋友開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db7e0db9d76f797707ab4dffb15786ec15429605","tid":337543,"uid":85819,"like":81,"dislike":9,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:30:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bcb104578c0ded6099c8b3af83598b9597d5329c","tid":337543,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:32:13.000Z","msg":"個銀碼係幾多"},{"pid":"a4603ebb8e9f1caccad4e0322e40700b85d2dd35","tid":337543,"uid":44454,"like":136,"dislike":2,"score":134,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:39:17.000Z","msg":"其實賠返個尿袋錢好合理，始終係交收嘅時候你冇辦法交出嚟，但之後搵返個尿袋，都應該屬於你"},{"pid":"d09dd7d9463162066af6ca318cb1432ffc7d46d5","tid":337543,"uid":70028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:40:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實賠返個尿袋錢好合理，始終係交收嘅時候你冇辦法交出嚟，但之後搵返個尿袋，都應該屬於你</blockquote><br />\n+1"},{"pid":"7138ff04147d2bf77b708e518cf315730546d78b","tid":337543,"uid":28031,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T12:53:50.000Z","msg":"細過400蚊咪可以要你賠囉<br />\n反而扣人工先犯法喎