d":75112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T19:21:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實賠返個尿袋錢好合理，始終係交收嘅時候你冇辦法交出嚟，但之後搵返個尿袋，都應該屬於你</blockquote><br />\n合理"},{"pid":"a4e923879e5fa2e9ba541dbf4a2b6cd2995c3aa9","tid":337543,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T21:19:44.000Z","msg":"搵個屌米應酬呢d 垃圾公司都費是<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26664030763acf741297623dde69f4a591cc19d6","tid":337543,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T22:56:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33b1787dfa34bcd32b92a2f46aa791fc226a1278","tid":337543,"uid":9614,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:06:46.000Z","msg":"不需此商品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c91135983c052f81394bef5023c20035c6f0036f","tid":337543,"uid":5053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:21:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不需此商品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n警報聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f76e53490b43d0590c6e4f5ab8666039542485","tid":337543,"uid":69215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:22:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫朋友開 <br />\n我FD就做緊HKTV既倉務員(暑期工)<br />\n佢平日既工作就係用部公司比既手機(連barcode機) 跟單執貨 <br />\n咁開工個陣佢會比埋尿袋廢事部機做做下冇電<br />\n收工個陣一次過還番<br />\n執完一張單既貨會入落個箱到比PACKING既部門 再分貨<br />\n<br />\n咁佢完單入箱個陣唔小心放埋個尿袋落箱送左去PACKING<br />\n但其實送到PACKING係每次都好易發視搵得到 尿袋入埋箱佢唔係第一個<br />\n咁間公司就好ON9 有條規則話如果收工還唔到尿袋 當你整唔見個尿袋<br />\n你就要賠返個尿袋比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n既然都搵得返 點解要賠呀 扣人工都合理D丫 家下要人捐成個尿袋比佢 間公司知唔知咩叫唔見左野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> :  乞兒公司ON9規則 搵得返賠佢老味最多咪唔做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 公司規則要跟足 樓主未返過工</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n返工最多賠$300"},{"pid":"9d88d1a09848a24c407ad19075d1fc9d1635fb8e","tid":337543,"uid":79761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:27:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢間公司係咁，不斷用唔同理由扣員工錢，早走早著啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不能認同更多"},{"pid":"c5df6a1367e98e42dbbc3015a80feeb6aadda84b","tid":337543,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:33:44.000Z","msg":"上年做嗰陣唔會借尿袋畀步兵架喎<br />\n新規矩嚟?<br />\n<br />\n睇住啲人拎住佢咁撚大碌scan槍<br />\n佢碌scan槍仲要只係用橡筋綁埋部小米電話+scanner一齊,一個唔小心就好鳩容易跌爛跌花,又要賠300<br />\n連接又閪 成日scan完但係部小米又顯示唔到你係scan咗<br />\n<br />\n睇住啲友仔執貨已經戥佢哋覺得麻鳩煩,而家仲要帶住個尿袋<br />\n戇鳩鳩"},{"pid":"891fb23010ae2a7926cb492832a310c5d73be8c0","tid":337543,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:35:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e8a70909edad763d5b20d78eacb1c8794564b182","tid":337543,"uid":87511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不需此商品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n警報聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢句不需此商品仲要係好有節奏咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f4798ccc0a5a3da132dfcd71c349071beb9904","tid":337543,"uid":70038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T23:40:44.000Z","msg":"點解唔可以比幾日deadline 佢，佢還唔返先賠，垃圾公司"},{"pid":"ef92d70c0ecfe5900deb2158e98187fed035371d","tid":337543,"uid":12317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T00:12:57.000Z","msg":"依間公司真係好垃圾 特別係個肥婆admin"},{"pid":"720d9c83c45a23691536bb2178019b3019da14d8","tid":337543,"uid":9614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"cite